---
title: Easy Chicken & Veggie Filo Pie with Sesame Seeds & Garden Salad
description: This cosy dinner packs in a veggie-loaded chicken base that's full of flavour, then tops off the whole dish with a
light and flakey filo pastry. Be sure to serve it fresh from the oven for an optimally crisp pastry!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

